description.narrative: Strengthen DHIS-2 System (development of dashboard, collection of real time data, technical support and coordination), which contributes to Community-Based Management Of Acute Malnutrition, Nutrition And Emergencies, Nutrition And Hiv, Treatment Of Severe Acute Malnutrition.
